			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2464547">
									

<p>Alright, so this is the GoI Format for Team Wayfarer (Eta-13) in the MTF Contest. First time making an GoI format article, but this was fun to make, so I might try my hand at it again in the future.</p>
<p>Special thanks to my teammates, DreamwalkerFae and kol aumer, for all their help shaping this.</p>
<p>Additional thanks to: Crayne, Metaphysician, minmin, Thekillerax, TwistedGears, thedeadlymoose, Randomini, MacLeod, Von Pincier, and djkaktus. All of whom took a look at this when it was a draft and provided a plethora of much needed feedback.</p>
<p>Hope you guys enjoy.</p>
<p>Conwell</p>

