			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2471917">
									

<p>Right &#8212; and Ways into the Library are often referred to as specifically as &quot;Doors&quot;, as a subset of Ways &#8212; but I think that the author's intent was &quot;these people are assuming/not assuming that any portal connected to the Library is a Way&quot; not necessarily &quot;Ways only connect to the Library&quot;</p>
